CLI Mode
Generate a key:

bash

python cryptix_perfect_final.py genkey --algo aes
Encrypt a file:

bash

python cryptix_perfect_final.py encrypt --file example.png --algo aes --key YOUR_AES_KEY
Decrypt:

bash

python cryptix_perfect_final.py decrypt --file example_enc_aes --algo aes --key YOUR_AES_KEY

GUI Mode
Run:

bash

python cryptix_gui.py
Use the dropdowns and buttons to encrypt/decrypt text or files.
